e.com/2023/11/24/23971647/black-friday-2023-robot-vacuum-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-26T11:00:21-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-26T11:00:21-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年网络星期一指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;产品从交付的盒子中冲出的明亮彩色矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/q_XE-_pYSlKHHvEiL0ZgT-JMPqE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72810993/236878_CYBER_WEEK_PACKAGE_AFern安德斯.5。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Aaron Fernandez 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p class=&quot;p--has-dropcap&quot; id=&quot;ZIwdcX&quot;>;让我们面对现实吧 — 黑色星期五和网络星期一是不再保留感恩节后的周末。通常被认为是一年中最繁忙的购物日在大流行后已演变为更加广泛的购物日，许多零售商早在十月就开始了假日促销活动。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5GjOZD&quot;>;尽管亚马逊秋季 Prime Day 活动刚刚结束，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/blackfriday&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href= “https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fshop%2Fdeals%2Fblack-friday&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com”rel=&quot;赞助的 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a>;，其他零售商开始发放他们的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971107/black-friday-2023-best-deals- tech-earbuds-gaming-tablets&quot;>;十月中旬黑色星期五优惠&lt;/a>;，大幅降价 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals -cyber-monday&quot;>;智能显示屏&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday&quot;>;降噪耳机&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/24/23971647/black-friday-2023-robot-vacuum-deals-cyber-monday&quot;>;扫地机器人&lt;/ a>;，以及假期前的许多其他技术。随着 11 月 24 日的临近，节省的金额继续增加，现在网络星期一即将到来，我们看到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple- AirPods-Charging-Latest-Model/dp/B07PXGQC1Q/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;AirPods...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href =&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939216/black-friday-guide-cyber-monday-tech-gadgets-2023&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23939216/black-friday-guide-cyber-monday-tech-gadgets-2023" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23939216/black-friday-guide-cyber-monday-tech-gadgets-2023</id><author><name>边缘员工</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-26T10:45:33-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-26T10:45:33-05:00</updated><title> Apple 设备上的“网络星期一”早期最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;iPhone 14 与苹果第二代 AirPods Pro 旁边的照片。两台设备都湿透了，上面有明显的雨滴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bNyAiPu5TSKszHxwDXB1HjujHLc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72895666/226285_AIRPODS_PRO_2_cwelch_001 5.5.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 第二代 AirPods Pro 网络星期一促销价不到 200 美元。&lt;/em>; |图片：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hjr3cC&quot;>;与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/2/2/23583501/apple-iphone -ipad-active-2-billion-devices-q1-2023&quot;>;超过 20 亿人&lt;/a>;使用其产品，可以肯定地说，苹果的产品是世界上最受欢迎的产品之一。因此，毫不奇怪，它们也是很棒的节日礼物——只要您能超越它们通常带来的高昂价格标签。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang &quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;MK5Pnu&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;2023 年网络星期一最佳早期技术您可以获得的优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971107/black-friday-2023-best-deals-tech-earbuds-gaming-tablets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The 100 美元以下的网络星期一最佳优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965961/black-friday-2023-tech-deals-under-100-cyber-monday&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;f5fVhl&quot;>;如果您错过了黑色星期五优惠，幸运的是，网络星期一优惠就在